language aliases note in order to support language detection on the internet we need ISO 639/3066 language codes as well as Microsoft and other variants of these syntax: alias,...=language string1|voice1;languageString2|voice2;...;languageStringN|voiceN note both language string and voice are optional however the | must be included even if no language string is present
